{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"article":{"authorCode":"admin","authorName":"孙天骁","classify":"生活类","content":"<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\">RT</span><br style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\">&hellip;&hellip;数学课上开始右手臂抽筋，接着全身瘫痪，痛苦不堪。好几次还叫了出来。。。</span><br style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\">老师给她的家长打了电话，后来小东撑不下去了，然后老师立即给120打了电话。五六分钟后，急救车赶到了，医护人员把小东抬上了担架，抬上了急救车，提前放学，老郭随救护车走了</span><br style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\">接着八九个同学商量去医院看她。我考虑后还是不跟着比较好。然后我给老妈和</span><a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/i/sys/jump?un=soffio%D0%A1%D3%EE\" username=\"soffio%D0%A1%D3%EE\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"at\" style=\"color: rgb(29, 83, 191); outline: 0px; position: relative; text-decoration: initial; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\">@soffio小宇</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\">打了电话，惊吓的我得到了一些安慰，然后我回家了&hellip;&hellip;</span><br style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\" /><br style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\" /><span class=\"edit_font_color\" style=\"color: rgb(225, 6, 2); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(254, 247, 231);\">上次我见到救护车可是死人了啊。</span><br style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-hei